ective of regularization methods).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Aug 2003 13:44:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Aug 2003 17:26:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 27 May 2004 05:09:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-09"}
